snippet.title: Breaking Taps
snippet.description:
Exploring material science and machining in a garage shop.

For more documentary-style narration and a wider exploration of everyday items under various microscopes, check out my other channel Micrographia.

Optical Microscopes:
- Amscope 40X-800X Trinocular Dual-illumination Metallurgical Microscope with Polarization
- Amscope 3.5X-180X Simul-Focal Stereo Zoom Microscope

Atomic Force Microscope:
- ICSPI nGauge AFM (100nm wedge tips and 20nm DLC tips)

Scanning Electron Microscope:
- Thermo Phenom XL G2 (BSD, SED and EDS)
